title: Sherman (2011) (Dragonz-C-T) cbr
description:
United States early 50s.
Mythical figure of the self-made man, Jay Sherman is to fill a man from nothing, he devoted his life and fortune to the success of his children, Robert and Jeannie. Then a candidate for president of the United States, his son is murdered before his eyes.
This murder is only the first act of retaliation many aimed Jay Sherman.
What he is accused? Who wants to assassinate him?

It seems that his past hides some gray areas on which the FBI agent Eva Cruz will have to light ...


enjoy
